[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あーはいはい！　ここでやるな、よそでやれ！\n酔っ払いでも酒場出て表でケンカするだろう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01433",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "なんだ貴様？　人間の分際で我らに意見する気か？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01434",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "管理者だかなんだか知らないけど、ここで暴れたら\nブラオールの港がぶっ壊れるだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01435",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "島国で海運機能がなくなったら、「管理」にも\n支障が出るんじゃないのか？　エルスたちもだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01436",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "当たり前だ。\nそれに、民間人に被害を出すわけにはいかん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01437",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "フン。わけの分からん理屈を並べて\n逃げようという算段であろう。その手には乗らぬぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01438",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "いや、乗ってやろう。確かにここで戦うのは\n野蛮がすぎる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01439",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01440",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "この男、ゼロを前にして怯まぬ、面白い人間だ。\nこういう手合いは逃げはしない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01441",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はは、男に見込まれても困るなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01442",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "それに、俺たちに負けた言い訳にされても困る。\nどうせ戦うなら、しっかり心を折らないとな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01443",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "この島より西、「雷鳴の島」と呼ばれる場所がある。\nそこで雌雄を決しようじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01444",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "雷鳴の島……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01445",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "常に鳴り響く雷に、雷で焼けた不毛の大地……\nおよそ人が住めないような島だ。近づく者すらいない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01446",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その過酷さは相当のものだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01447",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うぐぐ、そんなにヤバい場所で……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01448",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "「雷鳴の島」へ来い。来る度胸があればな。\nそこで俺たちに勝てばこの「九偉人図」はくれてやる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01449",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "もちろん、戦う意志のない者は来なくていい。\n俺は哀れな民草をいたぶるほど非道ではない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01450",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "たとえば、そこの女のような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01451",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ア、アタシは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01452",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ゼロ、行くぞ。ああ、食料だけは買い込んでおくか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01453",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我らが退屈せぬよう、すぐ来てほしいものじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01454",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "アルビーナ……\nうちのヘルトが酷いこと言ってごめん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01455",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01456",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ふう……なんとかやり過ごせたが、奴らはなんなんだ？\n前に見かけた時もそうだったが……危険な匂いがする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01457",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "協力を求めるにあたり、こちらの情報も開示しよう。\nお前ももう、他人事ではいられないだろう……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01458",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "昔から人類を影で操り、「管理」してきたパルメ族……\nあいつらを見なきゃ与太話で済ましてたんだけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01459",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "目の当たりにしたら、信じるほかないってことか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01460",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "彼らパルメ族、そして九偉人という枷から\n人類を解き放つために、ジョゼ、お前の力を借りたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01461",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "いいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01462",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……即答とはな。助かるが、いいんだな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01463",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。確かにいつもの俺なら断るとこだけど……\nここは、やらないと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01464",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "協力感謝するぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01465",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "存分に当てにしてくれ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01466",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "話がまとまってよかったです～！　そうと決まったら\n「雷鳴の島」への出航準備をしましょうね～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01467",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……あの連中を目の当たりにして、そのくじけなさは\n頼もしいというか、危なかっしいというか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01468",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふっ、ですね。それではいったん解散して、\n準備ができ次第また集まりましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01469",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]